snippet.title: Lysium: Stardiver | Overhaul Teaser
snippet.description:
We've updated Stardiver's art to 3x the original resolution and completely rewrote the engine to support it alongside many other new features. Here's a quick look at the Asteroid Farm to get the ball rolling!

https://twitter.com/Mawilo_Studio
